title: Is it normal to be placed a lot lower than where you were placed last season?

replies.body:
not really, but possible. My main (this account was Gold 5 last season) started provisionals in Iron 3, and finished Silver 2 (went 7-3).
My alt (was gold 4 last season), started provisionals at Iron 4, and finished Iron 1 (went 6-4).
